Package: satpoint
Type: Package
Title: Automates Extraction of Information From NETCDF Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Andrew", "Duncan", email = "andrew.duncan.ic@uhi.ac.uk", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7314-9629")),
    person("Annette", "Boerlage", email = "annette.boerlage@sruc.ac.uk",
    role = "ctb"),
    person("DECIDE", role = "fnd"))
Maintainer: Andrew Duncan <andrew.duncan@sruc.ac.uk>
Description: The satpoint package is designed to make extracting information
    from NetCDF files at specific geographic locations as easy as possible. 
    You provide some geographic data and an NetCDF file, satpoint will extract
    the variable data automatically.
